Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That form...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the extent of\Nthe rumored "Absolute Defense"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You were wearing sand, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your opponent's not just him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That attack just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been dangerous\Nhad I not been protected by sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My body is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just be a hindrance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're first, Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken out his spinal column?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:56.88,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,600)\pos(662,531)\3c&H000000&}Vengeful Strike!\NThe Bracken Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance of the Clematis Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A bone of the strongest calcification...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It will pierce you,\Nsand defense and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No time... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimate Defense: Shukaku's Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will\NKimimaro hold out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he should still\Nbe okay for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all I could with the treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's not nearly enough\Ninformation about his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be quite different\Nif we had something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Iike the medical history\Nand treatment data of his clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What came out after looking into it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was the bloody history of how\Nthe Kaguya Clan became just him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools who provoked the great land of\Nthe Village Hidden in the Mist into battle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with just their clan\Nand were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaguya Clan was\Na foolish clan that liked battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield was the only place\Nwhere they could be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was long ago when\Na simple-minded group
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that only enjoyed slaughter\Nwas acceptable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The times are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing something like fighting\Nonly with power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,against a governed organization\Nlike the Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be called an act of fools\Nrushing towards death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you saved only he\Nwho was the youngest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the most exceptional\Namong the Kaguya Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid possessed the power that\Nwould be feared even by the fighting clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems he was kept\Nin prison the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been a waste to let him... die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't want\Nthat rare Kekkei Genkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses a strong\Nand firm bone structure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and a defensive power to\Nrepel all kinds of physical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if turned to offense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the bones become\Na most powerful weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I've fought him once\Nthat I understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That sand shield is\Nan absolute defense, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that unusual form...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.\NThere's no way it'll be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered minerals with\Ngreat hardness from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,applied pressure with Chakra\Nand mixed them into the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You... that unusual Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kekkei Genkai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaguya Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ability which now\Nonly I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one of the clan, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll die out here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to sickness,\Nmy body will not last so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the clan will not die out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "Earth" Curse Mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can become a part of you,\NLord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get everything, Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's see the truth of\Nthis world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my "Vessel of Dreams".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They are presents from me.\NI hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather... die or obey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Obey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the best a team\Nof four can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask just once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you rather choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, we're the Sound Ninja Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not alone, you said...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As an existence shouldering\None part of Lord Orochimaru's ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remain inside\NLord Orochimaru's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru's brainwashing, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pitiful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I used my big moves too much.\NI don't have much Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amount of Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sink and confine you\N200 meters into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By the pressure of the sand\Nstuck to your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll soon be unable to move,\Nnot even a finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it...!\NThis time for sure you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bracken Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It is annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when waiting eagerly for\Nsomething you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking like\Nyou're humoring a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should know\Nthis the most, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can beat Kimimaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what hindrance\Nshould appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to do something like this;\Nvery impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was ride the sand\NI'm always controlling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to know how you use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At last... The destruction of\Nthe Leaf will begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Hokage...\NI'll teach you a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kimimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Kazekage of\Nthe Hidden Sand Village
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is no match against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro, it's thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro, so you can't go on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't be of use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no significance\Nto my living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your condition, Kimimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Destruction of the Leaf"\Nresulted in an unfortunate near-miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Sound Ninja Four\Nhave gone to pick up a new vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru's new\N"Vessel of Dreams".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru's brainwashing, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pitiful guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong... Far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no significance to living...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you might be able to discover\Nsomething interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,by continuing to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how you discovered that flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how I discovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "Earth " Curse Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With this... I can become\Na part of you, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get everything, Kimimaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's see the truth of\Nthis world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to discover\Nthe truth of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lord Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a persistent guy,\Nbut this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't ever come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not brainwashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That person...\NLord Orochimaru understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be? Has Kimimaro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The likes of Kimimaro makes\Nno difference now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... I can hardly wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come here even by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have been totally hammered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My sensei said it often...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck is also a part of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That backseat driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a backseat driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't good enough at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for you saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But please don't talk like that\Nabout my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you feel that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the honor of someone you revere\Nhas been hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you yourself are hurt badly\Nand become enraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The more important the person\Nyou revere is to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The clan won't die out...\NI'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remain inside\NLord Orochimaru's soul for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That person,\NLord Orochimaru, understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting for the sake of someone\Nimportant to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also the same\Nas Uzumaki Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the person who is important\Nto oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,might not always be "virtuous".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way someone evil\Ncan be thought of as an important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Even if you know they're evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't defeat solitude alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Comment: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:06.43,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED Start
