Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.82,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.36,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:23.16,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:28.80,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:34.21,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:40.14,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:45.81,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:51.93,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:59.00,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
